criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male or female patients aged ≥18 years;

          -  Patients with a Body Mass Index (BMI) included in the interval [18.5-33.0] kg/m²;

          -  Patients who received a primary kidney transplant at least 12 months prior to study
             entry

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Evidence or suspicion of ongoing or persistent, acute or chronic rejection;

          -  Requirement for dialysis within the six months prior to study entry;

          -  Glomerular filtration rate (GFR) <30 mL/min

          -  Pregnant or breastfeeding women, confirmed by a positive human chorionic gonadotropin
             (hCG) laboratory test;

          -  Intolerance to tacrolimus, excipients (including lactose, fructose or galactose), or
             similar products;
